360
00:16:27,170 --> 00:16:28,050
Of course not.

361
00:16:28,490 --> 00:16:29,810
Why did you ask me to change my route?

362
00:16:29,810 --> 00:16:30,940
It was a long detour.

363
00:16:34,040 --> 00:16:35,480
[Baby]

364
00:16:44,220 --> 00:16:45,250
He drove by that day

365
00:16:45,250 --> 00:16:46,680
