366
00:16:46,680 --> 00:16:47,080
Hello.

367
00:16:47,980 --> 00:16:48,420
Hello.

368
00:16:48,450 --> 00:16:49,210
We meet again.

369
00:16:49,210 --> 00:16:50,270
Yes, we meet again.

370
00:16:50,890 --> 00:16:52,290
There's one more person.

371
00:17:01,690 --> 00:17:02,490
Guess who I am.

372
00:17:05,290 --> 00:17:05,819
Duan Rou?

373
00:17:07,900 --> 00:17:09,300
There are only two words.

374
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:11,290
Did you need to think about it for so long?

375
00:17:11,290 --> 00:17:12,020
Captain Qin.

376
00:17:13,319 --> 00:17:13,740
No.

377
00:17:13,930 --> 00:17:16,210
I- I thought about it.

378
00:17:16,520 --> 00:17:18,920
At first, I wanted to call you Miss Duan Rou.

379
00:17:18,970 --> 00:17:20,430
But then I remembered you asked me

380
00:17:20,430 --> 00:17:22,300
not to call you "Miss," because it's too formal.

381
00:17:22,300 --> 00:17:23,849
So I had to switch.

382
00:17:26,410 --> 00:17:27,540
Why are you nervous?

383
00:17:28,770 --> 00:17:29,580
Who's nervous?

384
00:17:29,580 --> 00:17:31,780
I'm afraid I might say something wrong.

385
00:17:32,300 --> 00:17:33,430
Welcome to Gonghai.

386
00:17:34,390 --> 00:17:35,720
Thank you, Captain Qin.

387
00:17:38,120 --> 00:17:38,720
You drive.

388
00:17:38,740 --> 00:17:39,970
We'll take the same car.

389
00:17:39,970 --> 00:17:41,170
You two take that one.

390
00:17:41,330 --> 00:17:41,680
Okay.

391
00:17:42,210 --> 00:17:43,540
We'll take the same car?

392
00:17:43,960 --> 00:17:44,630
Calm down.

393
00:17:45,050 --> 00:17:47,090
You got scared twice within a minute.

394
00:17:47,090 --> 00:17:48,950
