395
00:17:50,080 --> 00:17:51,280
Who says I'm not calm?

396
00:17:52,460 --> 00:17:52,990
Let's go.

397
00:17:58,210 --> 00:17:59,070
Let's go first.

398
00:17:59,120 --> 00:17:59,450
Okay.

399
00:18:30,850 --> 00:18:31,980
Have you had enough?

400
00:18:32,220 --> 00:18:32,580
No.

401
00:18:33,560 --> 00:18:35,570
We haven't seen each other in over a month.

402
00:18:35,570 --> 00:18:36,970
I want to look at you more.

403
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:39,640
I'll take you to the town.

404
00:18:40,380 --> 00:18:42,110
Will you sleep with me tonight?

405
00:18:42,440 --> 00:18:42,880
Yes.

406
00:18:43,830 --> 00:18:45,100
Speak more gently.

407
00:18:46,850 --> 00:18:47,370
Yes.

408
00:18:49,760 --> 00:18:50,720
I miss you.

409
00:18:52,370 --> 00:18:53,100
I'm driving.

410
00:18:53,430 --> 00:18:54,430
Don't touch me.

411
00:18:54,490 --> 00:18:54,910
No.

412
00:18:55,090 --> 00:18:56,150
I want to touch you.

413
00:18:56,270 --> 00:18:57,870
I haven't seen you in a month.

414
00:19:18,010 --> 00:19:18,740
Captain Qin.

415
00:19:19,100 --> 00:19:19,900
Yes, I'm here.

416
00:19:21,900 --> 00:19:23,230
Where are we going now?

417
00:19:23,760 --> 00:19:24,640
A town.

418
00:19:25,530 --> 00:19:26,250
Police

419
00:19:27,090 --> 00:19:29,950
work in secured areas.

420
00:19:30,080 --> 00:19:31,280
It's not convenient.

421
00:19:31,850 --> 00:19:32,650
I understand.

422
00:19:38,450 --> 00:19:39,890
Can you play some music?

423
00:19:40,330 --> 00:19:41,260
Sure.

424
00:19:41,610 --> 00:19:42,010
Sure.

425
00:19:50,380 --> 00:19:51,700
It's quite hot here.

426
00:19:53,570 --> 00:19:54,210
It's okay.

427
00:19:54,790 --> 00:19:56,250
It's colder than Beijing.

428
00:19:59,880 --> 00:20:01,610
Are you usually busy with work?

429
00:20:04,010 --> 00:20:05,740
I'm usually quite busy at work.

430
00:20:09,730 --> 00:20:10,660
Are you thirsty?

431
00:20:12,120 --> 00:20:12,880
A little.

432
00:20:16,150 --> 00:20:16,950
Let me find it.

433
00:20:17,040 --> 00:20:18,770
I know this car better than you.

434
00:20:19,420 --> 00:20:19,880
Yes.

435
00:20:29,350 --> 00:20:30,730
Why aren't you saying anything?

436
00:20:30,730 --> 00:20:31,810
I keep talking.

437
00:20:31,810 --> 00:20:32,810
and you keep saying "hum".

438
00:20:32,810 --> 00:20:33,450
I thought

439
00:20:33,450 --> 00:20:35,050
you didn't want to talk to me.

440
00:20:35,930 --> 00:20:36,770
That's not it.

441
00:20:37,340 --> 00:20:38,270
My throat hurts.

442
00:20:38,760 --> 00:20:39,960
I can't really speak.

443
00:20:40,170 --> 00:20:40,900
Are you sick?

444
00:20:41,470 --> 00:20:43,200
Let me take you to the hospital.

445
00:20:44,150 --> 00:20:45,230
It's a minor illness.

446
00:20:45,230 --> 00:20:46,140
A minor illness will

447
00:20:46,140 --> 00:20:48,540
become a serious disease if you leave it be.

448
00:20:48,810 --> 00:20:49,980
You can't take it lightly.

449
00:20:49,980 --> 00:20:52,040
I've brought medicine, Captain Qin.

450
00:20:52,540 --> 00:20:53,760
I know what to do.

451
00:20:54,170 --> 00:20:56,020
You really don't need to go to the hospital?

452
00:20:56,020 --> 00:20:56,770
No.

453
00:20:58,610 --> 00:20:59,810
I think...

454
00:21:01,200 --> 00:21:02,930
if you don't feel well, just go.

455
00:21:03,710 --> 00:21:06,310
Are you always

456
00:21:06,800 --> 00:21:08,080
this fussy at work?

457
00:21:08,190 --> 00:21:08,680
I...

458
00:21:10,730 --> 00:21:11,740
I'm decisive.

459
00:21:14,180 --> 00:21:15,700
Decisive?

460
00:21:17,200 --> 00:21:18,610
I can't tell.

461
00:21:20,020 --> 00:21:20,500
Really.

462
00:21:21,330 --> 00:21:22,520
I'm always very firm

463
00:21:22,580 --> 00:21:23,460
with the team.

464
00:21:26,920 --> 00:21:28,720
You're taking it too seriously.

465
00:21:37,550 --> 00:21:38,310
Did you

466
00:21:39,330 --> 00:21:40,330
make a wrong turn?

467
00:21:41,290 --> 00:21:42,020
Impossible.

468
00:21:42,600 --> 00:21:43,930
There are no cars ahead.

469
00:21:48,660 --> 00:21:50,740
It seems I've really made a wrong turn.

470
00:21:50,740 --> 00:21:51,770
I got distracted

471
00:21:53,110 --> 00:21:53,970
talking to you.

472
00:22:10,360 --> 00:22:11,490
They're not there.

473
00:22:15,980 --> 00:22:16,760
Maybe he's nervous

474
00:22:16,760 --> 00:22:17,760
because he's with

475
00:22:18,050 --> 00:22:19,050
the girl he likes,

476
00:22:19,160 --> 00:22:20,630
so he's not keeping his eyes on the road.

477
00:22:20,630 --> 00:22:21,750
He likes Duan Rou?

478
00:22:22,550 --> 00:22:23,410
Did he tell you?

479
00:22:23,690 --> 00:22:24,290
No.

480
00:22:25,430 --> 00:22:27,000
But I've been working with him for a long time.

481
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:27,600
I can tell.

482
00:22:30,650 --> 00:22:31,650
I think

483
00:22:31,980 --> 00:22:33,820
Duan Rou likes him too.

484
00:22:34,290 --> 00:22:35,730
Why don't we set them up?

485
00:22:37,170 --> 00:22:38,100
I think we should

486
00:22:38,410 --> 00:22:39,890
let them go with the flow.

487
00:22:40,770 --> 00:22:42,170
Qin Mingyu is stationed at Qining.

488
00:22:42,170 --> 00:22:43,370
If they get together,

489
00:22:43,560 --> 00:22:44,840
it'll be a long-distance relationship.

490
00:22:44,840 --> 00:22:45,720
And this job

491
00:22:46,460 --> 00:22:48,260
basically has no vacation days.

492
00:22:48,450 --> 00:22:50,050
You have to think it through.

493
00:22:50,970 --> 00:22:52,730
But aren't you the same?

494
00:22:53,070 --> 00:22:54,790
After my mission, I’ll go back to Tianwen.

495
00:22:54,790 --> 00:22:55,720
He's different.

496
00:23:00,010 --> 00:23:00,970
It's a problem.

497
00:23:03,630 --> 00:23:05,030
Whatever will be will be.

498
00:23:05,340 --> 00:23:06,900
If they really fall in love,

499
00:23:07,650 --> 00:23:08,850
they will think about

500
00:23:08,850 --> 00:23:11,050
these practical problems themselves.

501
00:23:43,950 --> 00:23:45,220
He went the wrong way.

502
00:23:45,660 --> 00:23:47,190
I wasn't paying attention.

503
00:23:47,290 --> 00:23:48,570
It's your first time meeting.

504
00:23:48,570 --> 00:23:49,230
Keep the number of times

505
00:23:49,230 --> 00:23:51,290
