506
00:23:51,330 --> 00:23:51,990
Qin Mingyu.

507
00:23:52,490 --> 00:23:53,720
Don't embarrass the SWAT team.

508
00:23:53,720 --> 00:23:54,850
Who's embarrassing?

509
00:23:54,850 --> 00:23:56,040
Duan Rou's throat was inflamed.

510
00:23:56,040 --> 00:23:56,970
I got her water.

511
00:24:00,090 --> 00:24:02,210
Be careful of the sun, you might get freckles.

512
00:24:02,210 --> 00:24:03,720
It's okay. It's not far.

513
00:24:03,890 --> 00:24:05,650
You're different. Pay attention to this.

514
00:24:05,650 --> 00:24:06,890
Otherwise, you'll be depressed

515
00:24:06,890 --> 00:24:08,150
when you get freckles.

516
00:24:17,200 --> 00:24:18,730
You are quite considerate.

517
00:24:19,290 --> 00:24:20,490
No way, Officer Qin.

518
00:24:20,690 --> 00:24:21,950
You've just realized?

519
00:24:23,120 --> 00:24:25,580
I've been taking care of your son for so long.

520
00:24:25,610 --> 00:24:26,690
Have I made any mistakes?

521
00:24:26,690 --> 00:24:27,290
No, no.

522
00:24:27,290 --> 00:24:28,220
Absolutely not.

523
00:24:31,450 --> 00:24:32,780
Where do you want to eat?

524
00:24:32,970 --> 00:24:34,630
You have no recommendations?

525
00:24:34,750 --> 00:24:36,080
I don't come here often.

526
00:24:39,580 --> 00:24:40,170
This one

527
00:24:40,590 --> 00:24:41,390
