528
00:24:46,850 --> 00:24:47,490
Captain Lu

529
00:24:47,490 --> 00:24:48,410
looks like a normal person

530
00:24:48,410 --> 00:24:49,690
when he's with his wife.

531
00:24:49,690 --> 00:24:50,780
When he's alone,

532
00:24:50,810 --> 00:24:52,670
he's a machine-like workaholic.

533
00:25:09,030 --> 00:25:09,960
The second time.

534
00:25:11,110 --> 00:25:11,840
Cut the crap.

535
00:25:21,980 --> 00:25:22,990
You know this place well.

536
00:25:22,990 --> 00:25:23,590
You order.

537
00:25:24,870 --> 00:25:26,770
Did the doctor mention any dietary restrictions?

538
00:25:26,770 --> 00:25:27,130
No.

539
00:25:31,030 --> 00:25:31,960
I'll order then.

540
00:25:34,930 --> 00:25:35,790
Come back soon.

541
00:25:43,520 --> 00:25:45,080
Did you two not talk on the way here?

542
00:25:45,080 --> 00:25:46,740
Did you drive here in silence?

543
00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:48,330
-We talked.
-We talked.

544
00:25:51,850 --> 00:25:53,580
You're acting like strangers.

545
00:25:54,450 --> 00:25:55,250
That's him.

546
00:25:55,480 --> 00:25:56,740
I'm not being awkward.

547
00:25:56,840 --> 00:25:59,020
I have a sore throat, so I can't say much.

548
00:25:59,020 --> 00:25:59,820
It's my fault.

549
00:26:00,130 --> 00:26:01,500
I'm not good at holding a coversation,

550
00:26:01,500 --> 00:26:02,830
