00:27:11,930 --> 00:27:14,460
since their circumstances were compatible.

588
00:27:14,520 --> 00:27:17,980
It was mostly because he lacked experience in relationships.

589
00:27:18,600 --> 00:27:19,890
We win.

590
00:27:20,620 --> 00:27:21,850
So even though he looks

591
00:27:21,850 --> 00:27:23,410
like a single father—

592
00:27:23,980 --> 00:27:24,340
Wait.

593
00:27:24,380 --> 00:27:26,440
he actually doesn't know how to date.

594
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:29,630
Can't you say something nice?

595
00:27:29,630 --> 00:27:30,920
Who doesn't know how to date?

596
00:27:30,920 --> 00:27:31,530
Am I wrong?

597
00:27:32,420 --> 00:27:33,550
Should I say

598
00:27:33,580 --> 00:27:35,310
you've had a lot of experience with relationships?

599
00:27:35,310 --> 00:27:36,940
Who has been in a relationship?

600
00:27:36,940 --> 00:27:37,640
You have two options.

601
00:27:37,640 --> 00:27:38,300
Choose one.

602
00:27:42,010 --> 00:27:43,160
Have you ordered?

603
00:27:43,410 --> 00:27:45,070
Where do you think I just went?

604
00:27:45,520 --> 00:27:46,850
They came all the way here.

605
00:27:46,850 --> 00:27:47,670
We should order more.

606
00:27:47,670 --> 00:27:49,600
I'll go order a couple more dishes.

607
00:27:49,720 --> 00:27:50,250
Duan Rou.

608
00:27:51,500 --> 00:27:53,430
Thank you for taking care of my son.

609
00:27:54,170 --> 00:27:54,770
No need.

610
00:27:54,770 --> 00:27:56,010
It'll be a waste if we can't finish it.

611
00:27:56,010 --> 00:27:56,610
It's okay.

612
00:27:56,660 --> 00:27:57,950
We can take them home if we can't finish.

613
00:27:57,950 --> 00:27:58,880
It's not a waste.

614
00:27:59,210 --> 00:28:00,010
Let him order.

615
00:28:01,040 --> 00:28:02,640
He kept telling me about you,

616
00:28:02,770 --> 00:28:04,690
about how grateful he was towards you

617
00:28:04,690 --> 00:28:06,420
and how he couldn't express it.

618
00:28:06,480 --> 00:28:07,650
You wouldn't accept money,

619
00:28:07,650 --> 00:28:08,360
and he doesn't know

620
00:28:08,360 --> 00:28:09,490
how to choose gifts.

621
00:28:10,240 --> 00:28:11,170
But trust me.

622
00:28:11,800 --> 00:28:13,930
He is genuinely grateful towards you.

623
00:28:14,770 --> 00:28:16,160
There's no need for a gift.

624
00:28:16,160 --> 00:28:17,860
I'm taking care of his kid because I want to.

625
00:28:17,860 --> 00:28:18,920
If I didn't want to,

626
00:28:18,970 --> 00:28:20,050
no one can force me.

627
00:28:31,730 --> 00:28:33,790
I have something to discuss with you.

628
00:28:34,000 --> 00:28:34,530
Go ahead.

629
00:28:35,090 --> 00:28:36,470
I rarely see my wife.

630
00:28:36,940 --> 00:28:38,600
Let's sit at separate tables.

631
00:28:38,890 --> 00:28:39,610
Separate tables?

632
00:28:39,610 --> 00:28:40,130
Why?

633
00:28:40,970 --> 00:28:42,070
You guys can talk about the kid.

634
00:28:42,070 --> 00:28:44,070
We'll talk about our relationship.

635
00:28:49,690 --> 00:28:50,290
Right.

636
00:28:50,800 --> 00:28:52,120
They don't want to listen to us

637
00:28:52,120 --> 00:28:53,180
talk about the kid.

638
00:28:53,560 --> 00:28:55,000
They haven't seen each other for a long time.

639
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:56,280
Let's not disturb them.

640
00:28:56,280 --> 00:28:56,990
That's right.

641
00:28:56,990 --> 00:28:58,250
Let's sit separately.

642
00:28:58,550 --> 00:28:59,340
Time is precious.

643
00:28:59,340 --> 00:29:00,340
Don't disturb us.

644
00:29:01,980 --> 00:29:02,590
Okay.

645
00:29:02,730 --> 00:29:03,990
Let's sit separately.

646
00:29:09,920 --> 00:29:11,160
Duan Rou is very nice.

647
00:29:12,580 --> 00:29:14,980
She'd already gotten her marriage registered,

648
00:29:14,980 --> 00:29:16,570
but before they had the wedding,

649
00:29:16,570 --> 00:29:17,830
they got divorced over

650
00:29:17,990 --> 00:29:19,120
premarital assets.

651
00:29:19,400 --> 00:29:21,570
She wanted to sign a prenuptial agreement,

652
00:29:21,570 --> 00:29:22,700
but the guy refused.

653
00:29:22,720 --> 00:29:23,890
Later, she told me

654
00:29:24,170 --> 00:29:25,060
she wanted to find

655
00:29:25,060 --> 00:29:26,520
an independent boyfriend

656
00:29:26,610 --> 00:29:28,340
so that she could focus on work.

657
00:29:28,530 --> 00:29:30,250
She's on business trips

658
00:29:30,270 --> 00:29:31,600
for over 200 days a year.

659
00:29:31,730 --> 00:29:32,970
Also, she likes

660
00:29:33,020 --> 00:29:34,790
well-adjusted men

661
00:29:35,250 --> 00:29:36,850
who have their own pursuits.

662
00:29:37,000 --> 00:29:38,610
She doesn't want someone who

663
00:29:38,610 --> 00:29:40,130
constantly makes trouble

664
00:29:40,440 --> 00:29:42,700
over property, children, or housework.

665
00:29:42,960 --> 00:29:44,150
From this perspective,

666
00:29:44,150 --> 00:29:45,830
Qin Mingyu is perfect.

667
00:29:51,910 --> 00:29:52,950
Qin Mingyu

668
00:29:53,670 --> 00:29:55,400
has been conquered by Duan Rou.

669
00:29:55,840 --> 00:29:56,960
Thank you.

670
00:30:02,230 --> 00:30:03,430
Stop looking at them.

671
00:30:04,420 --> 00:30:05,040
Look at me.

672
00:30:05,400 --> 00:30:06,400
Look at your wife.

673
00:30:23,870 --> 00:30:24,470
By the way,

674
00:30:28,850 --> 00:30:30,450
I have something to tell you.

675
00:30:34,780 --> 00:30:36,800
These are my bank accounts.

676
00:30:36,940 --> 00:30:37,800
The passwords,

677
00:30:38,250 --> 00:30:38,920
ATM PINs,

678
00:30:38,950 --> 00:30:40,960
and online banking passwords are all here.

679
00:30:40,960 --> 00:30:42,820
The stocks and funds are here too.

680
00:30:44,410 --> 00:30:45,990
I don't know if you know how to handle these.

681
00:30:45,990 --> 00:30:46,560
You probably don't buy these,

682
00:30:46,560 --> 00:30:47,570
right?

683
00:30:49,720 --> 00:30:51,160
We have a safe at home.

684
00:30:51,840 --> 00:30:53,680
It can be opened by password or fingerprint identification.

685
00:30:53,680 --> 00:30:55,310
The password is your birthday.

686
00:30:55,310 --> 00:30:57,310
My most valuable things are inside.

687
00:30:59,210 --> 00:31:00,270
What are you doing?

688
00:31:00,800 --> 00:31:01,860
Listen carefully.

689
00:31:02,930 --> 00:31:04,410
There are medical risks

690
00:31:04,440 --> 00:31:05,910
in giving birth,

691
00:31:06,410 --> 00:31:08,090
for example, amniotic fluid embolism.

692
00:31:08,090 --> 00:31:09,590
Resuscitation is difficult.

693
00:31:09,590 --> 00:31:10,670
What if something happens?

694
00:31:10,670 --> 00:31:12,600
You need to know where to put these.

695
00:31:13,370 --> 00:31:15,360
You are not at home very often,

696
00:31:15,390 --> 00:31:17,520
and you don't care about these things.

697
00:31:19,380 --> 00:31:21,010
Don't look at me like that.

698
00:31:21,350 --> 00:31:22,610
If something happens,

699
00:31:22,850 --> 00:31:25,050
it'll be troublesome if you don't know.

700
00:31:29,380 --> 00:31:31,020
Don't look at me like that.

701
00:31:34,540 --> 00:31:35,890
I have another bank card

702
00:31:35,920 --> 00:31:37,050
with a million RMB in it.

703
00:31:37,050 --> 00:31:38,670
It's for my mother's retirement.

704
00:31:38,670 --> 00:31:39,530
Keep it in mind,

705
00:31:39,530 --> 00:31:40,590
but don't tell her.

706
00:31:43,080 --> 00:31:44,140
You worry too much.

707
00:31:45,390 --> 00:31:49,650
He who has no anxious thoughts for the future will find trouble right at hand.

708
00:31:49,980 --> 00:31:50,910
Do you regret it?

709
00:31:56,370 --> 00:31:58,770
You're only asking after I've married you.

710
00:32:06,320 --> 00:32:08,000
What I regret the most

711
00:32:08,920 --> 00:32:10,090
is not seeing you

712
00:32:10,090 --> 00:32:11,420
that year you came back.

713
00:32:11,570 --> 00:32:12,450
If I had seen you,

714
00:32:12,450 --> 00:32:14,310
I would have pinned you to the bed.

715
00:32:15,370 --> 00:32:16,130
I regretted this

716
00:32:16,130 --> 00:32:17,570
for a few days.

717
00:32:17,570 --> 00:32:18,570
I couldn't sleep.

718
00:32:21,600 --> 00:32:22,800
How old were you then?

719
00:32:23,570 --> 00:32:24,770
Would you have dared?

720
00:32:25,950 --> 00:32:26,690
Yes.

721
00:32:27,200 --> 00:32:28,330
If you dare, I do too.

722
00:33:09,400 --> 00:33:11,370
Supplements for anemia.

723
00:33:12,330 --> 00:33:13,790
Vitamins.

724
00:33:15,030 --> 00:33:15,650
And this.

725
00:33:18,680 --> 00:33:21,290
Since I got pregnant, I've had hypothyroidism.

726
00:33:21,290 --> 00:33:23,090
I have to take this to counter it.

727
00:33:23,310 --> 00:33:25,310
I asked the doctor if there are side effects.

728
00:33:25,310 --> 00:33:25,940
She said

729
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:27,800
there's a small probability

730
00:33:27,800 --> 00:33:29,160
it will affect the baby's intelligence.

731
00:33:29,160 --> 00:33:30,280
There's a certain chance

732
00:33:30,280 --> 00:33:32,450
the baby might inherit hypothyroidism.

733
00:33:32,450 --> 00:33:33,780
It's a very small probability.

734
00:33:33,780 --> 00:33:35,710
Don't worry. I'm taking medicine.

735
00:33:38,580 --> 00:33:39,840
I hope it won't happen.

736
00:34:57,180 --> 00:34:57,820
Lu Chen.

737
00:35:00,510 --> 00:35:01,550
I miss you so much.

738
00:35:02,530 --> 00:35:03,330
Do you miss me?

739
00:35:05,400 --> 00:35:06,290
Empty words

740
00:35:07,080 --> 00:35:08,210
are always the same.

741
00:35:08,380 --> 00:35:09,850
Do you miss me?

742
00:35:11,420 --> 00:35:11,810
Yes.

743
00:35:19,480 --> 00:35:20,720
Where are you going?

744
00:35:21,450 --> 00:35:22,490
I'm going to get some water

745
00:35:22,490 --> 00:35:23,550
for your foot bath.

746
00:35:27,440 --> 00:35:28,130
As expected,

747
00:35:28,130 --> 00:35:30,130
you should marry someone handsome.

748
00:35:30,390 --> 00:35:31,960
Handsome people have better tempers.

749
00:35:31,960 --> 00:35:34,290
Ugly men, on the other hand, are arrogant.

750
00:35:34,730 --> 00:35:36,110
He has a bad temper.

751
00:35:36,450 --> 00:35:37,650
When we were in school,

752
00:35:37,650 --> 00:35:39,250
he always pulled a long face.

753
00:35:39,400 --> 00:35:42,000
He terrified people without saying anything.

754
00:35:53,250 --> 00:35:53,580
Here.

755
00:36:25,750 --> 00:36:26,680
Massage my feet.

756
00:36:33,070 --> 00:36:33,570
Lu Chen.

757
00:36:35,240 --> 00:36:36,680
Where is your dog

758
00:36:36,720 --> 00:36:37,520
now?

759
00:36:39,480 --> 00:36:40,340
It's long gone.

760
00:36:40,750 --> 00:36:41,550
What about it?

761
00:36:42,630 --> 00:36:43,170
Do you remember

762
00:36:43,170 --> 00:36:45,430
the first time you wrote me a love letter?

763
00:36:48,400 --> 00:36:50,200
Are you sure it was a love letter?

764
00:37:02,250 --> 00:37:05,980
[2009]

765
00:37:15,480 --> 00:37:16,280
Hai Jianfeng.

766
00:37:17,920 --> 00:37:18,520
Chen.

767
00:37:18,870 --> 00:37:21,010
What are you doing so early in the morning?

768
00:37:21,010 --> 00:37:21,940
Walking the dog.

769
00:37:23,070 --> 00:37:23,870
You're early.

770
00:37:27,200 --> 00:37:28,330
Help me send a letter

771
00:37:29,610 --> 00:37:30,270
to Gui Xiao.

772
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:32,410
To who?

773
00:37:33,130 --> 00:37:34,590
Gui Xiao, from your class.

774
00:37:35,240 --> 00:37:36,370
You know each other?

775
00:37:37,480 --> 00:37:38,610
Give it to her for me.

776
00:37:42,450 --> 00:37:42,890
Go.

777
00:38:02,610 --> 00:38:03,210
Here.

778
00:38:04,720 --> 00:38:05,530
What?

779
00:38:06,880 --> 00:38:07,960
I saw Chen walking his dog

780
00:38:07,960 --> 00:38:08,960
on my way to school in the morning.

781
00:38:08,960 --> 00:38:10,620
He asked me to pass this to you.

782
00:38:50,310 --> 00:38:54,540
[Letter of Apology]

783
00:39:07,690 --> 00:39:08,090
Hello.

784
00:39:09,130 --> 00:39:10,590
You're not angry anymore?

785
00:39:10,940 --> 00:39:11,750
It's okay.

786
00:39:12,700 --> 00:39:13,970
In our class,

787
00:39:13,970 --> 00:39:15,050
people make a fuss

788
00:39:15,050 --> 00:39:16,610
over a boy and a girl talking.

789
00:39:16,610 --> 00:39:17,410
I'm used to it.

790
00:39:18,650 --> 00:39:19,930
You don't have to apologize

791
00:39:19,930 --> 00:39:20,690
for this.

792
00:39:21,680 --> 00:39:23,240
It's not true anyway.

793
00:39:23,950 --> 00:39:26,610
It's my fault for making people misunderstand.

794
00:39:29,440 --> 00:39:30,570
Have you recovered?

795
00:39:32,360 --> 00:39:33,820
How did you know I was sick?

796
00:39:34,670 --> 00:39:36,530
When I saw you along the corridor,

797
00:39:36,690 --> 00:39:38,420
you were holding back a sneeze.

798
00:39:39,520 --> 00:39:40,530
It was hard on you.

799
00:39:43,440 --> 00:39:44,650
You noticed?

800
00:40:31,880 --> 00:40:33,070
They're flirting.

801
00:40:41,010 --> 00:40:41,670
Captain Lu.

802
00:40:42,140 --> 00:40:43,800
Why didn’t you close the door?

803
00:40:44,210 --> 00:40:46,540
The open door isn't an invitation to peep.

804
00:40:46,670 --> 00:40:47,400
Do I need to peep

805
00:40:47,400 --> 00:40:48,660
when your door is open?

806
00:40:49,040 --> 00:40:50,250
Do not look at what is contrary to propriety.

807
00:40:50,250 --> 00:40:51,380
You came uninvited.

808
00:40:51,690 --> 00:40:53,150
I brought you some fruits.

809
00:40:53,610 --> 00:40:54,470
Did I ask you to?

810
00:40:54,740 --> 00:40:55,380
Enough.

811
00:40:55,410 --> 00:40:57,110
We're not the only ones living here.

812
00:40:57,110 --> 00:40:57,970
Close the door.

813
00:41:12,780 --> 00:41:14,030
You've washed your feet?

814
00:41:14,030 --> 00:41:14,890
Get some sleep.

815
00:41:16,420 --> 00:41:17,000
And then?

816
00:41:18,080 --> 00:41:18,610
And then?

817
00:41:21,530 --> 00:41:22,410
I'm off today.

818
00:41:23,500 --> 00:41:24,360
You look happy.

819
00:41:25,690 --> 00:41:27,290
I'm glad you're not leaving.

820
00:41:28,560 --> 00:41:29,530
Sleep with me.

821
00:41:31,800 --> 00:41:33,000
It's broad daylight.

822
00:41:34,300 --> 00:41:35,230
Let's take a nap.

823
00:41:37,990 --> 00:41:38,360
Okay.

824
00:41:39,990 --> 00:41:40,920
Let's take a nap.

825
00:41:46,820 --> 00:41:48,080
I've never lived here.

826
00:41:48,420 --> 00:41:50,240
I hope you can make yourself comfortable.

827
00:41:50,240 --> 00:41:51,480
Of course.

828
00:41:52,080 --> 00:41:53,130
I often go on business trips.

829
00:41:53,130 --> 00:41:54,060
I go everywhere.

830
00:41:54,370 --> 00:41:56,520
I'm not picky with food or accommodations.

831
00:41:56,520 --> 00:41:57,290
What else

832
00:41:57,310 --> 00:41:58,470
do you need?

833
00:42:01,070 --> 00:42:02,930
We don't need anything else here.

834
00:42:03,410 --> 00:42:04,140
That's good.

835
00:42:06,680 --> 00:42:08,280
Do you usually

836
00:42:08,350 --> 00:42:09,540
have a lot to say

837
00:42:10,130 --> 00:42:11,000
to Lu Yanchen?

838
00:42:12,010 --> 00:42:14,140
We've known each other for a long time.

839
00:42:14,330 --> 00:42:15,640
When guys get together,

840
00:42:15,640 --> 00:42:16,630
we talk more.

841
00:42:16,660 --> 00:42:17,860
I don't know

842
00:42:18,420 --> 00:42:20,080
what to talk about with girls.

843
00:42:20,480 --> 00:42:21,990
Are you tired?

844
00:42:22,170 --> 00:42:22,570
No.

845
00:42:24,590 --> 00:42:25,920
Will you show me around?

846
00:42:26,130 --> 00:42:26,620
Sure.

847
00:42:26,690 --> 00:42:29,090
Where do you want to go? I'll take you there.

848
00:42:31,610 --> 00:42:33,380
Is Qining nearby?
